Categorized GWAS data

Source: R/gwas_input.R
gwas_input.Rd

A list of length 7. The details of 7 objects are shown in the following: beta_pop object: BETA values across 7 cohorts. invse2_pop object: inverse of variance across 7 cohorts. marker_inf_pop object: basic information of each genetic variant, which consisting of MARKERNAME, CHROMOSOME, EA and NEA. corhort_count_filt object: the frequecies of each genetic variant present across 7 cohorts. sel_gene object: the genetic variants which are filtered out. pcs object: the axes of genetic variation which would be used in the meta-regression model. env object: the smoking proportions across 7 cohorts

gwas_input

Format

An object of class list of length 5.
